headline.main: Parise, Pominville Rejoin Minnesota Wild After Mumps Absence
headline.print_headline: Parise, Pominville Rejoin Minnesota Wild After Mumps Absence

lead_paragraph: Zach Parise and Jason Pominville have rejoined the Minnesota Wild after sitting out three games because of the mumps.
